text:
Chutpathi, tumhe pata nhi hoga lekin jabhi tum gaate the mai boht dhyaan se sunta tha kya hi mza aata hai sunne mai. Tum logo ke parties mai involve nhi ho paya kabhi butt kya hi mze karte the tumm. Tumse jab fir milenge to bhagwan kare aise mahaul bane ki jam karle tumhare sath. humour to hai hi alag level tumhara, i know i overdo it mostly but kya kare wohi aadat hai. i guess pehla shi wala interaction Hunterrrr movie se hi shuru hua tha, uske baad tum logo ki wing mai aake baith jaata tha jab bhi merko mze karne hote the bhai kya hi B1 mai premise-punchline chalta rehta tha. Ye yogi bsdka accept nhi karta tha mujhe lawdu(i know this :p) lekin kya farq padta hai, mujhe to bass hasna hota hai. Mai samne se call hamesha karta rahunga to contact mai to rahenge hi baaki covers daalte rho, i literally get chills sunke tum mano ya na maano isliye nhi ki boht acha gaate ho ya kuchh, i dont have the knowledge to comment on that, bas acha lagta hai mtlb boht acha lagta hai chutpathi.
kabhi bhi tumhe kaisi bhi madad chahiye ho to koi ho jo kar sake jaise tum rehte ho kisi aur ke liye yhi dua karte hai...

text:
Hiiiiiiii Pratigya !!
Kitne jokes aur kitna hasaya hai maine tum sab ko, are mai to thak hi gyaa.
"Sunn zara mere paas aa ab baithe hai ham bhi yaha" - Baarishein by Anuv jain, kitna sunaya hai ye 2 line maine tum logo ko. Haa i knoww bohot acha gaata hu mai, muh pe tareef nhi kar sakti thi tu. 2 trips and some nightouts maare, those were very much fun, mai to apna hasne ka quota pura karne aata tha you guyz know that, apni hi baat ki ab tak lol. Your 3rd year wala birthday was very noicee mze aaye the uss din. Ek yaadasht, Antaragni ground pe I did a stare and you looked at me at the exact moment, ye agar yaad hai to badi baat hai coz you know your raaste yaad rakhne wali memory. Gaane mai mze aate the tere and Rits and JD ke saath, Tanmay hame dekhta rehta tha bass xDD. Firse milunga mai "Quintessential Pratigya" se (its just my memory, can't help it).

text:
Hiiii Ritika!!
"Sunn zara mere paas aa ab baithe hai hum bhi yaha", kya meri madhur awaaz tujhe sunai de rhi hai...
Tere maze lene was one of the best things in the campus, everyone in chotu baddy group(this name lolol) knows that. Kya transformation tha tera yrr mtlb moti(i mean healthy obvio) se aur moti(no this time i mean moti only noob) ho gyi tu toh. We all were so hopeless for you hamesha hopeless hopeless chalta rehta tha tera. Now let's talk about the elephant in the room(lmao) tab se ussi ki baat ho rhi hai(pj credits-pratigya) On ocassions kya hi saj dhaj ke aayi thi tu, mai literally chakachaundh ho jaata tha ki XXXL size ke bhi kapde aate hai, mai aur jd dono fit ho jaate. Antrakshari wale games mai bohot shi mze aate the coz sab msti se gaate the aur tanmay chutiyo jaise dekhta rehta tha.
Wo jo bhi hotel tha(jisme top floor pe gaye the) wo sabse shi dinner tha apna and uss din ki photos <3<3. I guess uss din se ham sab zyada open and close(xDxD) ho gye the. memory of that day flashed  in front of my eyes, i hope tere bhi ho. Bhaiii itne jokes maare hai naa ki tu ready rehti thi joke ke liye ki joke maar le fir aage ka kaam karte hai bcðŸ˜‚ðŸ˜‚ðŸ˜‚. I was fucking blown away that day when you said you were waiting ki mai Hiiiii Ritika bolungaðŸ¥ºðŸ¥º. More power to you alwayssss.
